123
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,680
Whether you lie or not,

124
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,760
I can tell.

125
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,360
What did you see?

126
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:52,200
I'll tell you now.

127
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:57,360
Actually, my prophecy is accurate.

128
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,960
The thing is,

129
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,080
every time

130
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,560
when I see visions

131
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,440
about you,

132
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:09,920
they are unusual.

133
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:15,120
I saw rain, snow,

134
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:19,280
and someone's heartbreaking cry.

135
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,160
What else?

136
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,440
And...

137
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,800
Fire away.

138
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,720
And

139
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:32,400
