140
00:08:34,680 --> 00:08:36,080
I'll die for you?

141
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:42,120
I'll kill you now,

142
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:44,840
and your prophecy will be broken.

143
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,880
No.

144
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:51,640
It's not always that accurate.

145
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,720
It fails sometimes.

146
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,920
I'm influential in the imperial court

147
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,360
