General Hu seeks an audience
with His Majesty just now.

154
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:23,800
His Majesty summons you

155
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,040
to the inner hall immediately.

156
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:49,120
