157
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,880
You're indeed attractive,
Official Murong.

158
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:59,040
No wonder Princess Xueqing
takes a liking to you.

159
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:01,240
