except for you after returning home.

163
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:14,400
General Hu was so anxious about this.

164
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,440
There's no need for that, General Hu.

165
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,080
I'm a eunuch.

166
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,800
I can't marry a woman.

167
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,160
It doesn't matter.

168
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:25,920
The only thing that matters now
is to put that vow out of her head.

169
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:29,240
If Duke of Defender realizes this
when he returns,

170
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,480
I'm afraid that no one can save you

171
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,000
from his killing intention.

172
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:39,240
I see. So you came here tonight

173
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:41,880
to save my life?

174
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:46,440
Why do I care about you?

175
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:50,240
I care for the future of our country.

176
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,200
Princess Xueqing is of noble origin.

177
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:56,480
