than the adult emperor.

188
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:43,720
Not in a million years.

189
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,240
For my mother's death

190
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:48,160
and the sacrifice of
your aggrieved family,

191
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,760
