193
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,760
Oh, no. Crap.

194
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,640
He's going to kill me.

195
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,280
I shouldn't have told him.

196
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,480
This is my last hope.

197
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,240
I'm counting on you.

198
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:40,360
Spring breeze in warm air

199
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:43,520
